<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1565561.The_Essential_Haiku"><img alt="The Essential Haiku: Versions of Basho, Buson, and Issa" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1185287544l/1565561._SX98_.jpg" />
