<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/115392.W_D_Snodgrass"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1206627606p3/115392.jpg);'></div>
